<br>
  I have the biles, now I need to farm the threads.  First off, are the spiders that these drop off of the crystalline devourers (Invisible backstabbing ones), or can they drop off of any crystalline spider?  Second, how far into Velk's Labrynth does one need to travel to find them (at entrance?).  Third, is it possible for a lv 45 to solo them? I'm trying to get a feeling of resist rates on Conflag &amp; Immobolize and how frequent are adds?  Speed in collecting them is not an issue, still bringing up tailoring (currently 103) for the final combine (55 vial of viscious mana and silk to match waiting for me).<br>
